<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">Il modo congiuntivo</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        70
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Il <strong>congiuntivo</strong> è il modo dell'incertezza, del desiderio, dell'eventualità. Indica un'azione possibile o desiderata, ma non certa; esprime un'opinione o un dubbio. È formato da:
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-red-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>due tempi semplici</strong> → presente, imperfetto;</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>due tempi composti</strong> → passato, trapassato.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold mr-2">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Osserva lo schema del modo congiuntivo e completa le frasi coniugando il verbo <strong>leggere</strong> al tempo indicato.
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm md:text-base">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-amber-200">
            <th class="border-2 border-amber-400 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Tempi semplici</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-amber-400 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Tempi composti</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border-2 border-amber-300 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-2">Presente</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Spero che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-red-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32"
                       data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="legga" data-correct-answer="legga"
                       placeholder="........">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border-2 border-amber-300 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-2">Passato</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Spero che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32"
                       data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="abbia letto" data-correct-answer="abbia letto"
                       placeholder="........">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-amber-50">
            <td class="border-2 border-amber-300 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 mb-2">Imperfetto</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Speravo che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-red-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32"
                       data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="leggesse" data-correct-answer="leggesse"
                       placeholder="........">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border-2 border-amber-300 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-2">Trapassato</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Speravo che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-32"
                       data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="avesse letto" data-correct-answer="avesse letto"
                       placeholder="........">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Underline simple and compound tenses -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      <span>Sottolinea <span class="text-red-600">tempi semplici<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-red-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span> e <span class="text-blue-600">tempi composti<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span>.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Ci sembra che il dottore <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">abbia dato</span> una bella spiegazione.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Se Pablo <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">avesse saputo</span> che venivi anche tu, ci avrebbe raggiunto.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Che gioia sarebbe se tu <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">vincessi</span> una medaglia!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Non mi va bene che <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">passiate</span> tutto il giorno davanti alla TV.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3: Highlight correct form -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
      Evidenzia la forma verbale corretta.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Pensavo che Martina
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_1" value="faccia" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">faccia</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_1" value="facesse" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">facesse</span></label>
          più tardi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Mi pare che tu
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_2" value="abbia dormito" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">abbia dormito</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_2" value="avessi dormito" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avessi dormito</span></label>
          troppo poco: hai le occhiaie.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Credo che il signor Rossi
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_3" value="abbia deciso" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">abbia deciso</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_3" value="decida" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">decida</span></label>
          di cambiare casa.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Ora vorrei che
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_4" value="mangiaste" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">mangiaste</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_4" value="aveste mangiato" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">aveste mangiato</span></label>
          un po' di frutta.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700">• Se
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_5" value="guardassi" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">guardassi</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1"><input type="radio" name="ex3_5" value="avessi guardato" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avessi guardato</span></label>
          meglio, avresti visto anche tu quella macchia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Reference -->
  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-red-600 font-bold text-base md:text-lg">Esercizi pp. 165-167 e 169</p>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
